text: @UPSHelp I know things in NC are off cause of the hurricane, but my packages keep getting delayed and then just returned to the sender. Called your number today but the guy just read me what the tracking number says online and spoke over me the whole time. Can I get real help pls

@xWatchMeRisex I know how frustrating it can be to not get a package that you have been waiting on. If you would like us to look into this please DM us your tracking number, complete address, and phone number. ^AC
